node.text:
Stüssy & Our Legacy Workshop, available now worldwide.

Select bucket hats were individually hand-dyed in Los Angeles, California by Niki Tsukamoto at Lookout and Wonderland. Combinations of osage orange, chestnut bark, quebracho rojo, sappanwood, brazilwood, lac, organic indigo and myrobalan were used to achieve one-of-a-kind colors for the headwear. 

Each pair of swim shorts and every nylon canvas jacket has been repurposed from archival Our Legacy fabrics.
